des:
A series of daily motivational quotes, phrases and sayings from Gary Vaynerchuk, CEO and co-founder of VaynerMedia. Listen to Gary talk about Hustle, Self-Awareness, Self-Esteem, Empathy, Optimism, Gratitude, Patience, Legacy, Culture and more. Gary also celebrates various holidays for a unique surprise. Stay tuned and start listening today! 

Due to the nature of Gary's content, this Flash Briefing skill may contain profanity. That said, if you're not listening because of that, you're literally stopping at floor one instead of reaching the top ;)
